STEAMGAMERS.COM | MiniGames | *Funtastic* @ 72.26.196.164:27015
Mg_Pauls_Obstacle_Challenge Made by [SG] Paul This is a difficult obstacle map! The T's must work there way through the enitre map and make it to the end room where you can then do the bonus level! There is no afk killer on my map meaning if you die you can respawn by pressing m 1 1. The round ends when a T makes it to the end of the bonus level and presses the button! Server Settings Required: -mp_autoteambalance 0 -mp_limitteams 0 -sv_airaccelerate 100 The NoBlock script is also required. The Map is running on the following servers so far: -MiniGames Amusing 66.135.43.185:27015 -MiniGames Funtastic 66.135.43.185:27016 p.s. There are 6 hidden bombs in the map which 5 have cool trails on ^^ NOTE: Please do not rename this map as it may mess up the textures in future edits that I make. Enjoy!
